            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Hd1e108">Rubrica 13</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De laude et commendatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
      ¶ De laude et commendatione. Rubrica. 13
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/> <ref>Tob. hyst. c. 18.</ref> <quote>Lux impii ex
      <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>tinguetur: nec splendebit
      <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>flamma ignis eius.</quote> 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e128"> 
         <ref>/ 20. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e130">Laus im
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>piorum breuis est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p>
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/> <ref>Psalmista 32 pslamus</ref> <quote>Rectos decm laudatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e139">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
            <ref>¶ Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 27</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e143">Laudet te
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>alienus et non os tuum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e149"> 
       <ref>/ 24. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e151">Uir fidelis
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>multum laudabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e157">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
         <ref>¶ Cronica de nugis philosophurum. c. 6. scilicet de biante.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e161">Bias vnus de semptem sapiententibus ait: In
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>dignum virum ne laudes ob diuitias. <!--240.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="101-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e175">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
                <ref>¶ Aristotelis ethincorum vel. i. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e179">Uidetur omnio lau
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>dabile in quale quid esse: et ad aliquid qualr
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>habere laudari. Sunt laudes per relationem.
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>Laus est operum similiter et corporalium et animalium</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e189">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>
          <ref>/ Idem magnorum moralium. li. i. c. 42.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e193">Liberalis
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>est laudabilis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e199"> 
       <ref>/ 71. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e201">Laudabiles sunt pru
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>dentes. Laus virtus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e208"> 
         <ref>/ Idem retho. v l. i. c. 16</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e210">Laus est sermo elucidans magnitudinem vir
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>tutis. Commendatio operum est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p>
         <ref>/ Lib. 2. c. 9.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/> <quote>Laudare presentem adulationis est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e220">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
             <ref>¶ Iesus filius sirach. in ecclesiast. c. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e224">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>est speciosa laus in ore peccatoris. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e230">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               <ref>¶ Oratius in epistolis. l. i. e. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e234">Qualem commen
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>des etiam atque aspice ne mox
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>Incutiant aliena tibi peccata pudorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e242">
               <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>
             <ref>/ Libro scodo. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e246">Plenius equo
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>Laudat venales qui vult excludere merces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e252">
               <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>
          <ref>¶ Tullius retho. artis noue. l. 3. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e256">Non so
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>lum laudis causa rectum sequi conuenit: sed si laus
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>consequitur duplicatur recti appetendi voluntas</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e264">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
          <ref>/ Idem phylipicorum el. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e268">vt quondam morbo
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>aliqui ex sensus stupore suauitatem cibi non
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>sentiunt: sic libidinosi auari facinorosi vere
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>laudis gustum non habent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e279">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
          <ref>¶ Ouidius epistolarum. 12. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e283">Ut culpent alii:
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>tibi me laudare necesse est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e289">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
          <ref>/ Idem de ponto vel. 4. et fi. e. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e293">Excitat auditor studium laudataque virtus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>Crescit et immensum glora calcar habet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e301">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
         <ref>¶ Paulus apostolus. e. 2. ad corithios. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e305">Qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>gloratur in domino gloretur. non enim qui seipsum commen
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>dat ille probatus est: sed quem dominus commendat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e313">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
       <ref>¶ Seneca in epistolis. ad lucillum vel. 7. e. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e317">Quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>setaris quod ab hominbus his laudatus es quos
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>non potes ipse laudare. Qualis quisque sit sci
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>ens si quemadmodum laudet aspexeris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e327"> 
          <ref>/ Lib.
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>8. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e329">Magnisicum est laudari a laudato
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>virorlaude digno. Merentem laudare iusti
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>tia est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e339"> 
          <ref>/ Idem de tranquillitate animi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e341">Qui non
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>inter laudantium blandientiumque positus gre
        <lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>ges pistolimum: inde sibiipsi ipse assentatus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e350">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
          <ref>/ Idem de remediis fortuitorum. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e354">Displice
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>re malis laudari est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e360"> 
          <ref>/ Idem de moribus:</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e362">Neminem cito laudauerins: neminem cito
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>accusaueris. <!--240.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e374">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e378">¶ Plinins de naturali hysto. in prohemino.
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>Benignum est et plenum ingenii pudoris profi
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>teri per quos profeceris. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e386">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e390">¶ Ualerius maximus vel. 4. t. de paupertate.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>c. 4. Non est necessaria solide laudi cupidi
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>nis anxia diuitiarum comparatio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e398">
               <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e402">¶ Macrialis cocus vel vndique suscepto. c. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>Uituperat subito: subito qui laudat alebs.
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>Nulli credo decus laudari a turpibus herme
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>Sed nec laudari ob turpia credo decus
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>Premio vel laudes abnuimus sceleri. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e414">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e418">¶ Auctor scilicet de fortu. hone. vite. c. 2. Lauda
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>parce: vitupera percius: nam similiter reprehen
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>sibilis est nimia laudatio quam immoderata vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="60" break="no"/>tuperatio. illa siquidem adulatione: ista ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>lignitate suspecta est. Non quamultis: sed qua
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>libus placeas cogita. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e433"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e435"> 4. c. Sit tam triste ti
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>bi laudari a turpibus ac si lauderis ob tur
        <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>pia. Nec extollas quemquam nec deijcias. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e443">
               <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e447">¶ Cato capstolo. 2. Cum te aliquis laudat iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>dex tuus esse memento.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Plus aliis de te quam tum tibi credere noli. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e455">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e459">/ Capitulo 3
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Nec te collaudes necte culpaueris ipse
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>Hoc faciunt stulti quos gloria vexat ianis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e467">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e471">/ Capitulo. 5. et fi.
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>Laudaris quicumque palam quodcumque probaris
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>Hoc vide ne rursus leuitatis crimie dannes.
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>Parce laudato: nam quem tum sepe probaris.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Una dies quilis fuerit ostendet amicus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e483">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e487">¶ Boetius de disciplina scholarium: lib. 3
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Rerum effectus exhibtione operis declaratur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e493">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e497">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: lib. i. e. 2. Quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>maius queritur quam ibi inuenisse laudum testi
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>monia vbi gratificatio non potest esse suspe
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>cta. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e508"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e510"> 3. e. Crescere virtutes solent ad preco
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>nii fastigium. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e516"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e518"> Li. 8. e. 3. Cum successor am
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>plius laudari nititur precedentis fama letatur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e524">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e528">/ Lib. 4. e. 30. Perfectum opus suum laudat
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>auctorem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e534"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e536"> 31. e. Prudens frequentiam non re
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>spirituat hominum in qua se nouit esse laudan
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>dum. alioquin virtutibus fama tollitur si earum
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>merita in hominbus nesciantur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e546"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e548"> Li. 9. e. 22.
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>Magnus verecundie stimulus est laus pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>rentu dum illis non patimur esse impares quos <!--241.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="101-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>gaudemus auctores. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e565"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e567"> 25. e. et fi. Gloriosis
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>dominis gratiora sunt preconia quam tributa. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e574">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e578">/ Li. 11. e. 23. Iuste potiora consequitur qui de
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>commissa sibi negocii perfectione laudatur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e584">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e588">¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur facetus. c. 2. Alterius
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>laudes moderate dicere laudo.
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Sed proprias nemo si sapit ipse refert. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e596">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e600">¶ Andreas ad gualterium de amore: li. i. Cal
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>lidi videntur blandimenti obtinere commentum
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>laudes aspectum laudati prolate. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e608">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e612">¶ Mattheus vindoc. de hysto. tobie. c. 30.
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>Se laudi conformet opus: nisi facta marrites
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>Uerbis verba nocent friuola: fructus abest </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-d1e620">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d80273-Qd1e624">¶ Prouerb. vulg. Loura loda elimaestro
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>Chi lalda el mato fal saiire. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
